; The client live-data layer: the §5b merge store (DDP deltas → a per-collection Minimongo of
; winning documents, with per-field subscription precedence) and the Fur binding (a reactive
; `find` signal that recomputes as the store changes). Pure (fennec-mongo + Fur's isomorphic
; signals), so it runs native (for tests/SSR) and compiles to JavaScript for the browser client.
; The js_of_ocaml DDP WebSocket client + `subscribe` are a later addition. See DATAFLOW.md §7.
(library
 (name fennec_pulse_live)
 (public_name fennec.pulse.live)
 (libraries fennec-mongo.bson fennec-mongo.query fennec-mongo.minimongo fennec-mongo.bson_json
   fennec.fur fennec.ddp))
